<td colspan="2">Grenade launcher compatible with standard ammunition and a variety of other grenades like armour piercing, shape charge, incendiary, kinetic penetrator, gyrojet-variants, etc. Classified as a heavy weapon and therefore rarely used in fluid field operations. Equipped with a high capacity drum magazine, fires in semi-automatic fashion.</td>
