<td>[DATA REDACTED]</td>
<td>Various nozzles</td>
<td colspan="2">The Flamethrower FLW70 is being produced by the Foundation in Germany. Can be used with gaseous, liquid and pasty fuels. With a range of grips and cases, it is available in pistol- or rifle form and as secondary weapon for mechanical powered armor at an individual or squadron level.</td>
